Package: libappindicator0.1-cil
Section: cli-mono
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${cli:Depends},
Description: CLI bindings for libappindicator
 This package provides the appindicator-sharp assembly that allows CLI (.NET)
